OL,5, The father of a girl who took her own  
OL,6, life says cyber-bullying should be made
OL,7, a specific crime to protect children.  
OL,9,FMia Janin's parents had no idea she was
OL,10,Fbeing targeted on social media by      
OL,11,Fpupils at her London school before she 
OL,12,Fdied in March 2021, aged 14.           
OL,14,FFather Mariano Janin told the BBC's    
OL,15,FSunday with Laura Kuenssberg programme 
OL,16,Fnew laws were needed to tackle the     
OL,17,Fissue affecting young people globally. 
OL,19,FHe said it was time to be "more alert  
OL,20,Fand I would like the system to work".  
